--- @target: std.fs
Filesystem operations for reading, writing, and checking file paths.
---

--- @target: read_text
Reads the entire contents of a file as text.

@param path The file path to read from.
@return A result containing the file contents as text, or an error if the file cannot be read.
---

--- @target: write_text
Writes text content to a file, replacing its existing contents.

@param path The file path to write to.
@param value The text content to write.
@return A result indicating success or an error if writing fails.
---

--- @target: exists
Checks whether a file or directory exists at the given path.

@param path The file path to check.
@return True if the path exists, false otherwise.
---
